data.title: 准备以至少30秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: The picture shows a man is sketching outside. The scenery opposes the man is a green field with grass and trees, but the man is sketching human facial details. The man wears a black leather jacket, a pair of jeans, and he is sitting on a yellow chair. He is sketching under a blue broken umbrella, and he is imitating his sketching using a real photo on the left top of his canvas. There are a few finished sketchings placed in order on his right-hand side.
